URL: https://github.com/reisportela/xhdfe-xfe
BugReports: https://github.com/reisportela/xhdfe-xfe/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: C++17 compiler (GCC, Clang/AppleClang, or Rtools/MinGW),
    GNU make or Rtools make, optional OpenMP; optionally the NVIDIA CUDA
    toolkit for the Linux GPU absorber (build with XHDFE_ENABLE_CUDA=ON).
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.0), stats, utils
LinkingTo: Rcpp
